</nav></header><main aria-label="main content"><div class="speakable">
      <b data-is-speakable>What Happens In Your Brain When You Make Art : Shots - Health News</b>   <b data-is-speakable>Making art is fun. But there's a lot more to it. It might serve an evolutionary purpose — and emerging research shows that it can help us process difficult emotions and tap into joy.</b>
</div>
