<div class="storytitle">
      <h1>Feeling Artsy? Here's How Making Art Helps Your Brain</h1>
   <input type="hidden" id="title795010044" value="Feeling Artsy? Here's How Making Art Helps Your Brain" />
   <input type="hidden" id="shortTitle795010044" value="Feeling Artsy? Here's How Making Art Helps Your Brain" />
   <input type="hidden" id="modelFullUrl795010044" value="https://www.npr.org/sections/health-shots/2020/01/11/795010044/feeling-artsy-heres-how-making-art-helps-your-brain" />
