        <img src="https://media.npr.org/assets/img/2016/12/05/malaka_sq-9a89fec257c9924f5a083fa5cfffc2353a88c3d0-s100-c85.jpeg" class="img"  alt="Malaka Gharib 2016 square" />
      </a>
